<br />
If you had the chance to design a realisitic bard song (nothing with like 30 minute durations and 10k dmg dds) what would you want.
<br />

<br />
My personal idea would to have song that enhance benifical spells such as healing or buffs. we already have songs that enhance the dmg of casters why not enhance a priest ability to heal.
<br />

<br />
any other ideas and keep it realisitic please</span></td>
