				<td colspan="2"><span>I see a whole new line of songs.
<br />

<br />
<u>Harmony Line</u>
<br />

<br />
<b>Dak's Damaging Dirge in A</b>
<br />
(Percussion)
<br />
A damaging diddty that when song alone causes your target 95pts of damage over 18secs.  Damage increases as more parts of the Dirge are song by other bards.  (Damage does not increase if twisted by the same bard)
<br />

<br />
<b>Dak's Damaging Dirge in B</b>
<br />
(String)
<br />
A damaging diddty that when song alone causes your target 95pts of damage over 18secs.  Damage increases as more parts of the Dirge are song by other bards.  (Damage doesnot increase if twisted by the same bard)
