<b>Dak's Damaging Dirge in D</b>
<br />
(Brass)
<br />
A damaging diddty that when song alone causes your target 95pts of damage over 18secs.  Damage increases as more parts of the Dirge are song by other bards.  (Damage doesnot increase if twisted by the same bard)
<br />

<br />

<br />
