<br />

<br />
When three parts are sung the damage increases to 175 over 18secs.  Totalling 525 damage by the three bards.
<br />

<br />
Finally if all four parts of the Harmony is performed each bard would do 250 damage over 18secs.  That would make a total of 1000 damage by the four bards.
<br />

<br />

